Chris Ball made a video to say goodbye to his family before taking his life . 
 He told them they were not to blame for his disease and that he loved them . 
 He had been suffering from depression for two and a half years . 
 He was turned away from Brisbane hospital due to no beds 11 days earlier . 
 Brisbane man, 21, is the fifth family member to have committed suicide . 
 His mother Kerrie Keepa has started a petition to call on the government to allocate more beds for suicidal youths in hospitals . 
 